javase01.t06.logic

Class NoteBookManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • javase01.t06.logic.NoteBookManager

  • public class NoteBookManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The NoteBookManager class represents manager of NoteBook class. It include all methods to work with NoteBook class

    For example: 

         NoteBook noteBook1 = new NoteBook();
     NoteBook noteBook2 = new NoteBook();
     NoteBook noteBook3 = new NoteBook();
     NoteBookManager manager = new NoteBookManager(noteBook1);
     //...
     //Operation with notebook1;
     //...
     manager.manage(noteBook2);
     //...
     //Operation with notebook2;
     //...
     manager.manage(noteBook3);
     //...
     //Operation with notebook1;
     //...

    See Also:
    NoteBook, Note
